[
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "麻三爷不来了，以后由我代他。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 85,
    "line_end": 87
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "你干什么？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 109,
    "line_end": 111
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "郡马爷，你忘了规矩么？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 113,
    "line_end": 115
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "麻三爷呢，他为何不来？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 135,
    "line_end": 135
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "他躺在棺材里了，当然不能再来送你。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 137,
    "line_end": 137
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "麻三爷死了？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 139,
    "line_end": 139
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你的金牌是一百二十四号，你若然还不相信是王爷叫我来替代麻三爷的，你尽可以不乘我这辆马车。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 149,
    "line_end": 151
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我岂有不信之理。老哥贵姓？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 153,
    "line_end": 155
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "孟。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 157,
    "line_end": 157
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "你回来了？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 167,
    "line_end": 169
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "是。我回来已经有三天了。班大人，你好。",
    "tone": "平淡",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 177,
    "line_end": 179
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "好，我们都在挂念你呢，可惜麻三爷死了。他得的是什么病了？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 181,
    "line_end": 181
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "听说是绞肠痧，御医请来，已经断气。临时找不到适当的人，王爷叫我替他。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 183,
    "line_end": 183
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我已经知道了，王爷派来通知我的人刚刚才走。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 185,
    "line_end": 185
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "麻三爷是天亮时候死的，王爷叫孟老弟来接你，大约来不及另外派人通知你。你们没有发生误会吧？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 187,
    "line_end": 187
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "没有。",
    "tone": "尴尬",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 189,
    "line_end": 189
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "那马倒是很懂规矩的！",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 191,
    "line_end": 193
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你们两个都是稳重的人，我也料想你们不至于发生误会的。不过我因为孟老弟是第一次到研经院来，又是第一次和郡马一起办事，我总是有点放心不下，是以出来看看。现在看到你们依时来到，我就放心了。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 197,
    "line_end": 197
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "多谢班大人。没有事情了吧？我回去了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 199,
    "line_end": 199
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "请替我禀告王爷，院中有点小事，如果他这两天抽得出空闲的时间，就请他过来一下。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 201,
    "line_end": 201
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "过两天我再替你接风。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 203,
    "line_end": 205
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "这个人是谁？我以前好像没有见过。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 207,
    "line_end": 209
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "他是王爷最宠爱的家将。以前王爷最亲信的心腹是飞凤的父亲，他老人家阵亡之后就是这位老弟了，这位老弟姓孟名中还，说起来还是你死去的岳父临终之时向王爷保荐的呢，五年前正当你来到王府之前的一个月，王爷派他到蒙古办事，现在才回家，你当然是没有见过他了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 211,
    "line_end": 211
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "这，这未免太委屈他了！叫他给我驾车，我却又如何当得起？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 215,
    "line_end": 217
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "研经院是不能随便让人来的。每天给你驾车的这个差事也很重要呢！王爷如此安排，一定是经过再三考虑的，你无须心有不安。再说你是郡马的身份，他虽然是得宠的家将，也总还是要把你当作主子的。只要你对他表示一点尊敬，他是识得大体的人，我想他也不会感到委屈的的。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 219,
    "line_end": 221
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "听说潜龙最近又在大都出现了，你知道么？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 227,
    "line_end": 229
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "可有人见过？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 231,
    "line_end": 231
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "还是像过去几次那样，只是传闻而已，也不知是真是假。不过，这次的传闻却多点根据，你还记得那两个帮助你杀了'杨老板'的人吗？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 233,
    "line_end": 235
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "那两个人怎么样了？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 237,
    "line_end": 237
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "那人暗杀了，那人杀了他们之后，就用他们的血在墙壁上画一条龙。",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 239,
    "line_end": 239
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "哦，有这样的事情，我还未知道呢。",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 241,
    "line_end": 241
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "这也是昨晚发生的事情。我们猜想壁上所画的那条龙想必是'潜龙'所留下的记号。当然，也有可能是别人冒用'潜龙'的标记。不过，总是不可不防。因此，我揣摩王爷的用意，他派遣孟中还给你驾车，这是要多用一个得力的人来保护你的，郡马，你虽然武艺高强，但那潜龙神出鬼没，你若单独碰上了他，王爷和我都是难以放心。有孟中还和你一起，那就不怕潜龙了。",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 243,
    "line_end": 243
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "多谢王爷和班大人爱护之意。",
    "tone": "感激",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 245,
    "line_end": 245
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "卫士",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "孟大哥赌钱去了，和弟兄们闹得正欢呢，我替你找他去。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 287,
    "line_end": 289
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wei_shi",
    "text": "这位孟大哥冷口冷面，却和你们很合得来么？",
    "tone": "好奇",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 293,
    "line_end": 295
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "卫士",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "孟大哥是一个很和气的人呀，郡马怎么说他冷口冷面？他对我们从来不摆架子的。以前我们在王府执役，常常和他赌钱，但他到研经院来，这还是第一次，郡马今晚迟了个时辰回家，所以一班老朋友就趁此机会邀他相叙了",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 301,
    "line_end": 303
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "卫士",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "孟大哥，明天早些来，咱们赌个尽兴。",
    "tone": "豪迈",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 307,
    "line_end": 307
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "孟大哥，对不住，劳你久候了。",
    "tone": "歉意",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 309,
    "line_end": 309
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "没什么，我们做下人的本来是伺候人的，上车吧。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 311,
    "line_end": 311
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我今晚回家迟了，但却给你带了一位熟人来啦。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 323,
    "line_end": 325
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "参见格格，贺喜格格。格格大婚，小人还没有送礼呢。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 329,
    "line_end": 331
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "你这几年在什么地方？可成家了没有？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 333,
    "line_end": 335
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "小人这几年来都在蒙古，颠连大漠，异域穷荒，能保得余生归来已是万幸，哪还顾得了成家立室？",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 339,
    "line_end": 341
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "如果格格没有什么吩咐，我回去了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 345,
    "line_end": 345
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "你们今晚回来得迟，王府开饭的时间恐怕已经过了，你就在我们这里吃一顿饭吧。我的两个孩子你也还未曾见过呢。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 347,
    "line_end": 349
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "不，我在研经院已经吃过饭了，多谢你啦。改天我再来看小格格和小贝子吧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 351,
    "line_end": 351
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "听说他是你的爹爹遗书保荐给王爷的，你和他很熟吧？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 353,
    "line_end": 353
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "我们在乡下住的时候，他曾经做过我们的邻居，但不久就搬到他处去了。爹爹在他搬走之后，也不过一年就进了王府。我们只是小时候见过面，谈不上什么熟识。爹爹大约是后来在军旅之中再遇到他的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 355,
    "line_end": 355
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "是这样吗？怪不得你从来没有和我谈及这个人。假如是很熟识的人，你一定会和我提起了。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 359,
    "line_end": 361
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "在王府当差的人不计其数，我怎能都想起来和你谈说呢？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 363,
    "line_end": 365
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "是呀。我也只不过问问而已。你别多心。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 367,
    "line_end": 369
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "世雄，你今天研究那内功心法，想必是用神过度了。我替你添一炉香。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 381,
    "line_end": 383
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "这是上好的安息香，你好好安息吧。一觉睡到大天光，精神就会好了！",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 395,
    "line_end": 397
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "飞凤，当真是你？唉，你，你怎能如此冒险出来？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 419,
    "line_end": 421
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我知道你会在这里等我的。我不出来见你一面，我也不能安心！",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 423,
    "line_end": 425
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "飞凤，你不顾危险，出来看我，我是感激得很，但给郡马知道，事情可就要闹大了。我不能玷污你的名誉，你，你还是回去吧。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 429,
    "line_end": 431
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我已经用上了'黑酣香'，他这一觉，不到明日日上三竿的时候，是决不会醒来的了。",
    "tone": "低语",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 433,
    "line_end": 435
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "你这几年过得怎样？郡马对你可好？",
    "tone": "关心",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 437,
    "line_end": 437
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "好——也还好。但你知道，在我的心中，是决没有第二个人可以替代你的位置的。我，我是出于无奈，才嫁了他。那时你又在蒙古，没有谁人可以帮我。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 439,
    "line_end": 441
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我那时即使不在蒙古，也帮不上你的忙的。你不能负王爷养育之恩，王爷也决不会让你嫁给一个马夫。过去的事，还是不必再说了吧。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 443,
    "line_end": 445
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "中还，你为什么要来给他驾车，这未免太委屈你了。",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 447,
    "line_end": 447
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "这是我自己请求的。我来了三天，正想不出有什么法子可以见你一面，恰巧麻三爷死掉。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 449,
    "line_end": 451
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我知道，你这样做全是为了我的原故。但你可得小心点儿，他，他是一个很精明的人。",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 453,
    "line_end": 453
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "你可曾向他透露过我的来历？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 455,
    "line_end": 455
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我怎会，连王爷也不知道你是汉人。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 457,
    "line_end": 457
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我跟了王爷之后，一直都蒙王爷重用，这都是要感谢你的。",
    "tone": "感激",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 459,
    "line_end": 459
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我可有点后悔将你荐入王府呢，当初以为可以等待机会，你得了王爷的重用，我就可以求王爷允许咱们的婚事，哪知道今天弄成了这样难堪的局面！",
    "tone": "苦笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 461,
    "line_end": 463
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "现在我也有点后悔回来了。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 471,
    "line_end": 471
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "这几年你在蒙古怎样，听说王爷对你的功迹很是满意。",
    "tone": "关心",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 473,
    "line_end": 473
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "没有什么，苦是苦一点，但我是愿意替王爷办事的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 475,
    "line_end": 475
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我好似听到什么声息？",
    "tone": "疑惑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 479,
    "line_end": 481
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "想你是疑心所至，他已经熟睡，郡马府中并没有第二个轻功高明的人。而且这个时候又怎会有人到这里来？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 485,
    "line_end": 487
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "今晚也许不会是他。但咱们这样下去，总有一天会给他发现的。",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 489,
    "line_end": 491
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "我明白。我也正想和你说：你知道我的心里是只有你的，可是我现在有了子女，我爱你，我也爱他们。中还，你原谅我，如果我没有子女，我一定会跟你私奔的。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 493,
    "line_end": 493
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "飞凤，你回去吧。以后我不会再找你了。你不怪我？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 495,
    "line_end": 495
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我只有感激你，感激你今晚不顾一切出来见我。有此一面，我受的什么苦也值得了，我，我但愿你家庭美满，夫妻和好，不再以我为念。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 499,
    "line_end": 499
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "你有什么心愿，用得着我的么？",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 501,
    "line_end": 503
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "我得你的帮忙很多，已经是感激不尽了。此次回来，只为见你一面，别无奢求。",
    "tone": "感激",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 505,
    "line_end": 505
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "好，我去了。你，你自己珍重。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 507,
    "line_end": 507
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "珠玛，是你！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 515,
    "line_end": 517
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你想不到我会来找你的吧？",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 521,
    "line_end": 523
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "飞凤呢？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 525,
    "line_end": 525
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你一见我，就问妻子，不觉得有点对不住我吗？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 527,
    "line_end": 529
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "珠玛，你是应该知道我这门亲事实是身不由己的，亏你还有心情和我一见面就开玩笑。",
    "tone": "苦笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 535,
    "line_end": 537
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "我知道，当然我不会怪你。我还要祝贺你呢。你若不是郡马，焉能进得了研经院？而且你这位妻子，才貌双全，也的确是很不错呀。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 539,
    "line_end": 541
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "这可不是开玩笑的事情，飞凤到底怎么样了？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 543,
    "line_end": 543
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你放心，我怎会杀了你的妻子，让你做不成郡马。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 547,
    "line_end": 549
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "那么她到哪里去了？你又是怎么进得来的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 551,
    "line_end": 551
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你不必追问她了，总之她不会这样快回来就是。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 553,
    "line_end": 555
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你这几年来研究穴道铜人的秘密和陈搏的内功心法，成绩可是很不错呀。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 561,
    "line_end": 563
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "你怎么知道？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 565,
    "line_end": 565
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "若然你的内功不是比前精进，我虽有解药，你也不会这样快醒来的。她用的是黑酣香，我用的却并非对症的解药。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 567,
    "line_end": 567
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "珠玛，你还没有告诉我，你是为什么而来的呢？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 569,
    "line_end": 569
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "那两样东西，你得手没有？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 571,
    "line_end": 571
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "差得远呢！虽然在研究上有点成绩，但穴道铜人的图解我见到的只有七张，内功心法，更是今天才开始看到一篇。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 573,
    "line_end": 575
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "那不成，你必须在一个月内，全部拿到手里！这是命令！",
    "tone": "严肃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 577,
    "line_end": 577
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_zhu_ma",
    "text": "哦，原来是他们派你来做我的帮手的！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 579,
    "line_end": 579
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "谈不上帮手，我是来给你接赃的！",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 581,
    "line_end": 583
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhu_ma",
    "speaker_name": "珠玛",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "这里我不便久留，我走了。你快快睡下，不可露出丝毫痕迹。决不能让你的妻子有半点怀疑。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 585,
    "line_end": 587
  }
]